title: shooting
---
body:

## checklist for shooting

- resolution
- frame rate
- white balance
- ISO / gain
- picture style
- shutter speed
    - 24 fps → 1/50
    - 60 fps → 1/125
- focus
- exposure
- audio

## settings

- AF mode - Quick / Live
- AF during movie - enable
- Movie exposure - manual
- grid display - grid 1 (1/3 - thirds)
- highlight tone priority - (disable)
- auto lighting optimizer (off / low / standard / strong)
